                <h1 class="white-text">1. KING ‚ôî</h1>
              </td></tr>
              <tr><td>
              <p class="white-text">Chess is won by checkmating - trapping - the king. Although the king is the most important piece, it‚Äôs not the most powerful. The king can move to any square that‚Äôs directly next to it: up, down, sideways or diagonal.</p>
              </td></tr>
