                <h1 class="white-text">2. QUEEN ‚ôõ</h1>
              </td></tr>
              <tr><td>
              <p class="white-text">The queen can move forwards, backward, sideways, and diagonally like a king. However, unlike the king, the queen can move as far as it wants to in each of these directions. </p>
              </td></tr>
              </table>
            </td>
            <td><img class="board" src="/assests/chess/queen.png"></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>
              <table class="table">
              <tr><td>
                <h1 class="white-text">3. ROOK ‚ôú</h1>
              </td></tr>
              <tr><td>
