              <tr><td>
                <h1 class="white-text">4. BISHOP ‚ôù</h1>
              </td></tr>
              <tr><td>
              <p class="white-text">The bishop can move diagonally like a queen, but not forward, backwards or sideways. Each side starts with two bishops, one on a light square and one on a dark square. </p>
              </td></tr>
              </table>
            </td>
