                <h1 class="white-text">GETTING OUT OF CHECK üèÅ</h1>
              </td></tr>
              <tr><td>
              <p class="white-text">When you are in check you must escape check. The ways to get out of check are to move the king, block the check with another piece or to capture the checking piece. </p>
              </td></tr>
              </table>
            </td>
